codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand Latin vocabulary. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. Syra: "Nōlī ~!" Quīntus: "Nōn fleō, ~ [= quamquam] dolōrem gravem ~." Choose from this set of possible answers [ aegrōtus latere laevō, recumbit dēnuō, percutit frangere, strepitum continuō, sibi dolōrem os, flēre etsī patior] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-ada-001' where ANSWER in [ 'aegrōtus latere laevō', 'recumbit dēnuō', 'percutit frangere', 'strepitum continuō', 'sibi dolōrem os', 'flēre etsī patior']
